input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/european_football_2.sqlite" "
SELECT T.team_long_name, COUNT(*) as home_defeats
FROM Match M
JOIN Team T ON M.home_team_api_id = T.team_api_id
WHERE M.season = '2015/2016'
  AND (M.home_team_goal - M.away_team_goal) < 0
GROUP BY T.team_long_name
ORDER BY home_defeats ASC
LIMIT 20;
"

-- Find teams that played home matches in 2015/2016 but had 0 home defeats
SELECT T.team_long_name, 
       SUM(CASE WHEN (M.home_team_goal - M.away_team_goal) < 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as home_defeats
FROM Match M
JOIN Team T ON M.home_team_api_id = T.team_api_id

GROUP BY T.team_long_name
ORDER BY home_defeats ASC
LIMIT 20;
"
